    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "The exocrine glands of the mammae that produce milk in females, and are composed of lobules, alveolar ducts and alveoli.,Glandular organ located on the chest. The mammary gland is made up of connective tissue, fat, and tissue that contains the glands that can make milk."
  } ],
