  "http://desiree-project.eu/bckm#NCI_DEFINITION" : [ {
    "@language" : "en",
    "@value" : "A carcinoma of the breast characterized by pools of mucin and islands of malignant squamous cells.  Mucoepidermoid carcinomas of the breast are extremely rare."
